# Commit Strategy

> **Always-on merged rule:** `.cursor/rules/maintainer-delivery-loop.mdc` — use that for enforcement in chat; this file remains a focused reference.

- Use focused commits with clear intent.
- Keep commit messages concise and reason-oriented.
- Do not batch unrelated changes in one commit.
- Preserve reviewability and rollback clarity.

